 explosives and equipment.\n\n\u2022 Take note of simulated wind and target distance with the wind meter and spotter scope. Calculate physics-based bullet drop and time-to-hit to improve your accuracy.\n\n\u2022 Use stealth to sneak up behind enemies with a silent knife kill. Or go head-to-head against enemies that will take cover and attempt to flank your position.\n\n\u2022 Randomized Enemy positions and doors, making each play-through an unknown challenge.\n\n\u2022 Non-linear maps give players an endless variety in how they choose to infiltrate and complete missions. Enter buildings through doors, climb ladders to reach rooftops, or climb through windows. The choice is yours.\n\nTactical Assault VR is currently an Early Access release and is updated regularly.", "short_description": "Tactical MilSim CQB (Close Quarters Battles) in Virtual Reality"}]}, "developer_name": "Twisted Barrel Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://twistedbarrelgames.wixsite.com/tactical-assault-vr/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Twisted Barrel Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://twistedbarrelgames.wixsite.com/tactical-assault-vr", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "707998687088613"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1357851021858876"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "828997436054349"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1773876819610591"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1357851021858876"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1730185200, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1357851021858876"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8685584458165942", "version": "0.8.0"}, "id": "1336107373548228", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5190911237633299", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8685584458165942"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1336107373548228"}]}, "change_log": "Operation: HAMMER FIRE\nThe uploaded data along with intel gathered from various ground sources has allowed us to pinpoint the exact location of the enemy leader. Located within a mountainous region is a compound where the enemy leader resides. Our first attempt to take him down has failed.\n\nMission:\n\u2022 Destroy the downed helicopter by planting C4 onto it\n\u2022 Eliminate the HVT (High-Value Target)\n\u2022 Exfiltrate\n\nAt long last, it's finally here! The Compound mission, titled \"[b]Hammer Fire[/b]\", is loosely based on a real-life mission that took place in Abbottabad, Pakistan in 2012.\n\nOperators will have to make their way through a steep-inclined, treacherously large town and push towards the compound where the HVT resides. You'll find yourself transitioning from large, open space to claustrophobia-inducing, shoulder-to-shoulder walls.\n\nDestroy the remains of the downed helicopter and carefully place your shot when taking down the HVT.\n\nHammer Fire boasts the highest enemy count between all previous missions and has the most intense fire-fights you'll experience in virtual reality.\n\nLIGHT MACHINE GUNS\nGive 'em hell with the new LMG class of weapons that include the FNMAG, Minimi, and PKM light machine guns. Utilize the bi-pod for increased accuracy or spray-and-pray as you lay down suppressive fire.\n\nHARDCORE MODE\nTest your reflexes against Enemy Ai that have increased vision, increased accuracy, faster first-shot reaction times, and use the SCAR-H. Utilize cover and communicate effectively with your team... or fail. Cry about it.\n\nMORE AVATAR AND WEAPON CUSTOMIZATION!\n[img]{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/43730144/bda5e2903543bd65c8be6f654de85cc8050a91cf.gif[/img]\nMore avatar customization options, weapon sights, and foregrip attachments along with updated designs throughout.\n\nWeapon and Utilities Additions/Updates:\n\u2022 Added FNMAG LMG (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added Minimi LMG (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added PKM LMG (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added TA31 + RMR 4x ACOG (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added ACRO red dot to pistols (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Added VGMod3 grip and Hand Stop grip to foregrip selections (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Replaced \"Aimdot\" with Romeo red dot (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Replaced/Updated OKP7 model and reticle (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Replaced USP45 with HK45 (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Replaced airsoft red dot sight with COMP M4 (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Updated 4x ACOG model (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Updated EXPS3 and G43 magnifier models (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Updated Foregrip models (modeled by Puddle_NL)\n\u2022 Updated new Breach Charge mechanics (pull the pin to set off the breach charge fuse)\n\nAvatar Additions/Updates:\n\u2022 Added Casual T-Shirt outfit to Avatar Customization\n\u2022 Added new Camo patterns to Avatar Customization (designed by Puddle)\n\u2022 Added More Head/Face selections\n\u2022 Added Camo Plate Carriers + Camo helmet to Avatar Customization\n\u2022 Updated Helmet and Headset model to Comtac style headset (designed by Puddle)\n\nQoL (quality-of-life) Additions:\n\u2022 Added Force Grabbing option in Settings menu (Enabled by default). Gain additional reach when grabbing weapons, magazines and utilities\n\u2022 Added Watch/Compass side preference in Avatar Customization Menu\n\u2022 Added Crouching Vest Pullback toggle in Settings. On by default.\n\nMultiplayer Additions:\n\u2022 Added Vote-Kicking System. A kicked player is banned from the room for the duration that the room is live\n\u2022 Added current Map ID to Room Listings within lobby rooms list (ie IS == Incoming Storm)\n\u2022 Added PvP Auto-Team Balancing (player will automatically join the opposite team if the chosen team is at capacity)\n\u2022 Added Direct Action Multiplayer Coop Lobby (Skip the training map and head straight to mission select and Start) Preferred for players who don't want to deal with squeakers, trolls, griefers and want to play missions.\n\u2022 Added: Knife Kills now count as kills or team kills\n\u2022 Added: Sledgehammer kills against EnemyAi now count as kills\n\nOther Additions/Updates:\n\u2022 Added bHaptics support for both PCVR and Stand Alone Quest\n\u2022 Major doors re-work with massive under-the-hood improvements\n\u2022 (Quest) Added Foveated Rendering for improved performance (lowered resolution at screen edges)\n\u2022 (Quest) Stand-alone players can now disable the documentary camera rendering for improved performance through Main Menu > Settings > Graphics > RenderDocCam toggle. Especially useful for Quest 2 players.\n\u2022 Added Hardcore Difficulty - enemy accuracy, reaction time, health and vision increased, UI elements reduced, more enemies, weapon variety...because the \"EnEmIeS aRe ToO eAsY\"... I want taste your tears!!!!\n\u2022 Improved enemy ai target selection over the network\n\u2022 Performance optimizations and improvements", "created_date": 1729972448, "id": "8685584458165942", "version": "0.8.0", "version_code": 300, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8685582798166108"}, "asset_files": {"count": 32}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5190911237633299", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8685584458165942"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1729867027, "id": "8677598062297915", "version": "0.8.0", "version_code": 299, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8677596555631399"}, "asset_files": {"count": 32}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5190911237633299", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8685584458165942"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1729621552, "id": "8658966624161059", "version": "0.8.33b", "version_code": 298, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8658964630827925"}, "asset_files": {"count": 32}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5190911237633299", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8685584458165942"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1729620409, "id": "86588855408